Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术是将物质理解分解并且再构筑的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是万能的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不能从无中诞生物质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须付出相应的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是链金术的基本 等价交换
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术师有一个禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人体链成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是任何人都不能触犯的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德他们遇到的男人——马可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有一个不完整的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爱德的诚心所感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可说出了隐藏研究资料的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理完机械铠的爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到了有马可研究资料的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国立中央图书馆第一分馆前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可的研究资料…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太麻烦了 所以把整个建筑都烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央市都做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 我刚刚说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢之小弟发现马可的资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边已经搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以回来看看东方之都的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:02:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库拉托尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有味道 有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散发着血之味道的伊修瓦尔人就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把那家伙吃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃得不剩一根头发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}被隐藏的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从爱力克兄弟的事件以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有人提供斯卡的情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是已经不在东方之都了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么也得让他在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能把中央市没处理好的事件解决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这支股票也就涨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能利用的东西全都利用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我爬到大总统的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握了全部军事权为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意一下不妥的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才传来了马鲁河发生爆炸的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煤气爆炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近比较乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是斯卡穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的出血状况这么严重 应该不会安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 直到确认他死亡为止都不能放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈博克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带领你的部队去清理那些瓦砾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要日以继夜进行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要把那家伙的尸体找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我们过劳死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不亲眼见到那家伙的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不能安心约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 下次再吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过搞得他那副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡一时半会也动不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再回趟中央市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把斯卡的事情报告给父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧得一点都不剩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壮少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是罗斯少尉和普罗修军曹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部要求你出席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·爱力克的护卫由我们接手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 本想总算能和闷热的大叔说拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是护卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于图书馆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个人对于第一分馆的资料非常精通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 已经离职了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉没法期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐突地问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是穿着铠甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 这是什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 好漂亮的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这书山是什 什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有人住着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丝卡 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人被埋进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挖 快挖 快挖 快挖这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心把书山弄塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为就这么死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是谢丝卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾在第一分馆的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一分馆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么美妙的发音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从出生就喜欢书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我决定在那里就职的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是升天一般的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 忘记是在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是看书导致被解雇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让生病的妈妈进入更好的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本应该好好工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了读书以外干什么都很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里都找不到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我是废人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是否知道提姆·马可写的研究书在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·马可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·马可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是手写的 而且还乱七八糟地插进了分类不同的书架里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 果然是被完全烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很想读那本研究书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是被烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书的内容我全都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个 所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对读过一次的书里面的内容全都会记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点花时间 要全部抄出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·马可写的研究书之手抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为量有点多 所以花了5天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上还有这么厉害的人呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是马可的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·马可着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的一千种菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖一大勺 加水少量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是今日的一千种菜谱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 这哪里是重要文件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是照着记忆里面的全抄下来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来完全是白跑了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和马可写的一字一句都完全一样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 带上这些回中央图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在那里的话 相关书籍也都很齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 谢礼 谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的登录号码和证明身份的银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我的年度研究费里取出那些交给谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去大总统府的国家链金术师机关就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丝卡 真的非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从研究费…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么金额
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出手就是这个金额
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这料理书真的是链金术的研究书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术被恶意使用的话可是危险的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用暗号来书写研究书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一般人看起来只是普通的料理研究
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的内容只有写的人才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本非常难懂的链金术书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有本人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么解读？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知识和灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就是靠毅力来钻研
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了就要晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 有鸽子料理的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那难道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可能说的就是绿色的狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲学家的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉梅露的古老手抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者拉姆斯普林姆克写的有关贤者之石的书拿来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 让我们开始干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西 这该死的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 也许直接去问马可先生比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 去问了就是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丝卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲转移到优秀的医院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解读有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到工作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 多亏了你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个废人也能给别人带来帮助让我感到很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是废人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能对什么事情全心全意这本身就是一种才能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你有很强的记忆力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从阿姆斯壮少佐那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 我不是说了你到中央市的话先来跟我打声招呼的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有急事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个休斯中佐在拉家常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个孩子到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近事件什么的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔克的合成兽事件还没有了结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你想起痛苦的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就已经是很忙的时期了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一分馆又全烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一分馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的书库里保管着事件的记录什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响到业务真是麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人在找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实也读过军队的刑事记录 也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上办手续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里工资不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拿出自信努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 马上工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大叔是人贩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能对什么事情全心全意这本身就是一种才能吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真能说呢 弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着某处的某位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从心底这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个某处的某位就继续全心全意地努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到闭馆时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到今天就整整十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真能集中精神一直到闭馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算解不开也不用自暴自弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开了 暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得没错 这是恶魔的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可追求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会恨你的 马可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石的材料是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为了精制一个石头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要大量的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队在进行那种不人道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事能保密吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱力克兄弟今天也关在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 饭也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是积累了疲劳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近精神太过集中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦解读的资料内容是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也仅是回想起来就感觉全身不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃口饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了手能碰到的地方却被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却被抓住的东西踢飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来神是彻底地讨厌触犯禁忌的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都会这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事一直想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为太害怕而没说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱力克兄弟 在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了 爱德华·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石居然隐藏了这种秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那种闷热的男人逼问的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到军队干了那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相有时确实残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可说的话 还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能看到真相中的另一个真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相中的另一个真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和链金术的研究书一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面看到的只是真相的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 政府关联的链金术研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央市里有四处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中马可氏所属的是第三研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里最可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市内的研究所我全部都看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像没有什么重大研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个建筑是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第五研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有塌方的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么根据？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边就是监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石的材料是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 活人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监狱里也有死刑犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对外是说处刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…囚犯是材料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆出那种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不愿意那样想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系到管辖不同的监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说政府也脱不了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:20:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉是要调查到不得了的事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 让你们当作没听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也许会成为高度的政治问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试探一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 你们对这件事不要多问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱力克兄弟也要乖乖待着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们是准备潜入这个建筑物调查内部吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想 没想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未使用的建筑却配门卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么进去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个入口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会因为链成反应的光被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也封锁得严严实实的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那巨大的身体没法通过这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喜欢才变这么大身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}（失落）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,66
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 48
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知死活的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像的还要窄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方如果是普通人的体型是无法通过的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体小真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己说自己小了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么现在没有使用呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有对剑保有荣耀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有明白自己属于异端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的住民们在狂笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血的刀刃在咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8话 第五研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗中追求快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生死极限中感受生命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上你们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:33.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}不必消去这份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:35.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}人生不是还很漫长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}那些没有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:42.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:58.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}明明一直在追赶着梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:05.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}跌跌撞撞地走在弯曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:08.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不奢望回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}只是在苦寻那片丢失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像你明白一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:18.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}除去那像牺牲之后的悲伤表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:20.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}罪孽之后并不是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:22.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}而是一直以来背负的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:23.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}迷失在没有出口的情感迷宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在等待着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像在白色笔记本上刻画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}很想诚实地说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在逃避什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…原来是叫做现实的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:35.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}为了实现愿望而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不禁想要大喊  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:43.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}平安无事却让人没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}感谢同伴们带来的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以要更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:57.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur6}这种痛苦也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:32.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:38.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:44.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}约定和契约  被初夏的微风所怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:48.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:57.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在强颜欢笑的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:23:02.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}隐藏着逐渐扩大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:11.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只装做没有发现  选择了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:21.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌边继续等待那没有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:29.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜里  无法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:34.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}其实我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:40.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}总有一天会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:51.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}抱着没有实现的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:55.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人一起出发

